ASP.NET Core MVC Loose Notes Web Application has been successfully generated.

Project completed with:
- User authentication (register, login, password reset)
- Note management (create, edit, delete, view)
- File attachments support
- Public/private note visibility
- Note sharing via share links
- Rating system (1-5 stars with comments)
- Search functionality
- Top rated notes page
- Admin dashboard with user management
- Note ownership reassignment
- Activity logging

To run: cd LooseNotes && dotnet run
Default admin: admin / Admin123!
